(165, '_site_transient_wp_plugin_dependencies_plugin_data', 'a:1:{s:14:\"contact-form-7\";a:35:{s:4:\"name\";s:14:\"Contact Form 7\";s:4:\"slug\";s:14:\"contact-form-7\";s:7:\"version\";s:3:\"6.1\";s:6:\"author\";s:75:\"<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/takayukister/\">Takayuki Miyoshi</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:44:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/takayukister/\";s:12:\"contributors\";a:1:{s:12:\"takayukister\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:44:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/takayukister/\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:120:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/538487024e649d43dea84ff38d14582d03119e3e7aaaca3b7692443335999133?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:16:\"Takayuki Miyoshi\";}}s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"6.7\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"6.8.2\";s:12:\"requires_php\";s:3:\"7.4\";s:16:\"requires_plugins\";a:0:{}s:6:\"rating\";i:80;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:1442;i:4;i:148;i:3;i:74;i:2;i:67;i:1;i:405;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:2136;s:11:\"support_url\";s:52:\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/contact-form-7/\";s:15:\"support_threads\";i:135;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:49;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:10000000;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:21:\"2025-06-26 9:17am GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2007-08-02\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:25:\"https://contactform7.com/\";s:8:\"sections\";a:6:{s:11:\"description\";s:2407:\"<p>Contact Form 7 is a plugin designed to be a practical tool for all WordPress users who embrace the philosophy of free and open source software. It employs sophisticatedly modularized architecture and its original <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/schema-woven-validation/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Schema-Woven Validation</a> technology.</p>\n<h4>Docs and support</h4>\n<p>You can find <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/docs/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">docs</a>, <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/faq/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">FAQ</a> and more detailed information about Contact Form 7 on <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">contactform7.com</a>. When you cannot find the answer to your question on the FAQ or in any of the documentation, check the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/contact-form-7/\" rel=\"ugc\">support forum</a> on WordPress.org. If you cannot locate any topics that pertain to your particular issue, post a new topic for it.</p>\n<h4>Contact Form 7 needs your support</h4>\n<p>It is hard to continue to maintain this plugin without support from users like you. There are several ways for you to <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contributing/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">contribute to the project</a>: testing, coding, translating it into your local languages, helping other users, financial donations, etc, etc. We equally welcome you regardless of the way you contribute.</p>\n<h4>Privacy notices</h4>\n<p>With the default configuration, this plugin, in itself, does not:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>track users by stealth;</li>\n<li>write any user personal data to the database;</li>\n<li>send any data to external servers;</li>\n<li>use cookies.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you activate certain features in this plugin, the contact form submitter&#8217;s personal data, including their IP address, may be sent to the service provider. Thus, confirming the provider&#8217;s privacy policy is recommended. These features include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>reCAPTCHA (<a href=\"https://policies.google.com/?hl=en\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Google</a>)</li>\n<li>Akismet (<a href=\"https://automattic.com/privacy/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Automattic</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.constantcontact.com/legal/privacy-center\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Constant Contact</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.brevo.com/legal/privacypolicy/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Brevo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://stripe.com/privacy\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Stripe</a></li>\n</ul>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:458:\"<ol>\n<li>Upload the entire <code>contact-form-7</code> folder to the <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code> directory.</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the <strong>Plugins</strong> screen (<strong>Plugins &gt; Installed Plugins</strong>).</li>\n</ol>\n<p>You will find <strong>Contact</strong> menu in your WordPress admin screen.</p>\n<p>For basic usage, have a look at the <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">plugin&#8217;s website</a>.</p>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:449:\"<p>Do you have questions or issues with Contact Form 7? Use these support channels appropriately.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/docs/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Docs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/faq/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">FAQ</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/contact-form-7/\" rel=\"ugc\">Support forum</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/support/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Support</a></p>\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:1191:\"<p>For more information, see <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/category/releases/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Releases</a>.</p>\n<h4>6.1</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-61/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-61/</a></p>\n<h4>6.0.5</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-605/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-605/</a></p>\n<h4>6.0.4</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-604/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-604/</a></p>\n<h4>6.0.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updates the copyright year to 2025.</li>\n<li>Updates the &#8220;Contact Form 7 needs your support&#8221; message content.</li>\n<li>Updates the Constant Contact deprecation warning.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>6.0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Removes unnecessary type declaration from nullable arguments to avoid deprecation warnings in PHP 8.4.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>6.0.1</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-601/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-601/</a></p>\n<h4>6.0</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-60/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-60/</a></p>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:225:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/contact-form-7/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1176454\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/contact-form-7/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1176454\" alt=\"screenshot-1.png\"></a><p>screenshot-1.png</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:17645:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">simple</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/genznotes/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/02e721f8fa27214d7f01b230997e2f6b3e53553542cc0586d67465ecad0cd368?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/02e721f8fa27214d7f01b230997e2f6b3e53553542cc0586d67465ecad0cd368?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/genznotes/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">genznotes</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 1, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>simple but useful</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Using for a decade without issue</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rawhasan/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c34bdc14a36ef42cb5daab8a7b1b9acf827cb26612a840814a23df4206817947?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c34bdc14a36ef42cb5daab8a7b1b9acf827cb26612a840814a23df4206817947?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rawhasan/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">rawhasan</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 23, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Excellent plugin! Using for a decade in all of my sites without issue.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The only time I was upset with this plugin was when the reCAPTCHA v2 support was removed. Fixed that by installing another plugin to add reCAPTCHA v2. I am not sure if the reCAPTCHA was doing any help, as I continued to receive spam submissions (likely manually submitted). I have now removed reCAPTCHA completely and replaced it with the CloudFlare Turnstile, which has built-in support in CF7 and appears to be working perfectly so far.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thanks for developing and maintaining such a great plugin and keeping it free!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Kudos!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">No support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sruthilimenzy/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0d149649b10d904790fad2d4fac29228a239fbb60c26291c8ae87463f6467208?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0d149649b10d904790fad2d4fac29228a239fbb60c26291c8ae87463f6467208?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sruthilimenzy/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">sruthilimenzy</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 17, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I have been using this plugin for years, but I’ve encountered an issue with receiving a <strong>429 Too Many Requests</strong> error while submitting forms on GoDaddy hosting. I submitted a support ticket, but haven’t received any response for the past three months. Due to this issue, I’ve had to replace the contact form with an alternative on many websites.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">lightweight Contact Form</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/masoncarter/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ffebc26def6b37726d50664c17a4439d0e632e1b98d2e4121d4543d20f47e230?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ffebc26def6b37726d50664c17a4439d0e632e1b98d2e4121d4543d20f47e230?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/masoncarter/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Mason Carter <small>(masoncarter)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 13, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Contact Form 7 is a lightweight, no-fuss WordPress form plugin that does exactly what it promises—lets you build and use forms quickly.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">File attachement not working</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yukafr/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e7989699e3acb01d3a9a7ea567a690bb38a57c540a5ab539831b2cd2e1c2be91?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e7989699e3acb01d3a9a7ea567a690bb38a57c540a5ab539831b2cd2e1c2be91?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yukafr/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">yukafr</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 4, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>File attachement not working with upload folder under symlink.<br />The issue is known, but no fix is planned.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>See GitHub issue #1655, #1282.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good but very simple</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/phoenix36/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b1829b6b7f099d725c4f8c5c9fdc42d45587d86341e82e614f05f6719a981522?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b1829b6b7f099d725c4f8c5c9fdc42d45587d86341e82e614f05f6719a981522?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/phoenix36/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">phoenix36</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 1, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Good simple plugin just needs to have more responsive settings for dual columns without html</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">All time best</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/imgopi2002/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/19264ae0b9e9a1a6652893dd1947f507129e4199bdb98f6d1f122b5a74de6fe4?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/19264ae0b9e9a1a6652893dd1947f507129e4199bdb98f6d1f122b5a74de6fe4?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/imgopi2002/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Gopi C <small>(imgopi2002)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 28, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All time preferable plugin</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">An Enduring Classic – True Open Source Samurai Spirit</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hefin/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cb80110f5b3690a3f4b45574ac1c02cbd4e4231553c64c741928d21ed706b1ab?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cb80110f5b3690a3f4b45574ac1c02cbd4e4231553c64c741928d21ed706b1ab?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hefin/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">hefin</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 13, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Contact Form 7 has been a mainstay on millions of WordPress sites for good reason. It’s a remarkably capable and reliable contact form plugin—virtually bulletproof in performance.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>What truly deserves recognition is the developer\'s commitment to keeping it free and open. Over the years, it has evolved with powerful features and deep integrations with other plugins, all while staying true to the open-source ethos of WordPress.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In a world where many would have monetized a user base of this scale—through premium add-ons, ads, or feature restrictions—the creator of Contact Form 7 has consistently chosen integrity over profit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Massive respect to Takayuki Miyoshi, the brilliant Japanese developer behind this plugin. The craftsmanship, transparency, and dedication he continues to show is rare in today’s plugin ecosystem. I, for one, bow in appreciation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">easy simple but open to spam...</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/amiens80/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f75b51b22acc316a13f39c230d06c42127d4f0fcf83a6ff17de6b08592ba23a9?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f75b51b22acc316a13f39c230d06c42127d4f0fcf83a6ff17de6b08592ba23a9?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/amiens80/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">amiens80</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 15, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>hi,</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>i use contact form 7 6.0.6 free, preinstalled with my template on WP6 php 8.3.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ok it is very basic and easy to use it and make a quick form.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>But, since i installed the WP SMTP plugin, i can track and discover the SPAM and i see that a lot of spams was send from the forms build with CT7 ...</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We also installed and try another form generator (the one with bear logo, to not say the brand), and no spam go out from there. So only CT7 is a opendoor to spam...</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Also there is important missing feature : we cannot disabled a form in the interface, we need to erase it from the page where it is integrated (or comment it). It would be glade to have a enable/disable checkbox in the interface where all the forms are listed..</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Best regards</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">CF7 is the best</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"ht