(4928, 656, 'my_money_4_image_content_content_description', 'A valid ID and an active account are required. Additional documents may be requested for verification.\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Employed individuals</h3>\r\nA valid ID, proof of income, and an account application form are required.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Self-employed individuals</h3>\r\nProvide a valid ID, business registration documents, and proof of income, such as an ITR.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Overseas Filipino Workers (OFWs)</h3>\r\nPresent a valid passport, overseas employment contract, and authorization documents (if applicable).</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Corporations or partnerships</h3>\r\nSubmit business registration documents, SEC/DTI certification, and a board resolution.</li>\r\n</ol>'),
