(6312, 834, 'my_money_4_image_content_content_description', 'Provide a valid ID and a completed application form. Additional verification documents may be required.\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Employed individuals</h3>\r\nProvide a government-issued ID, proof of employment, and a completed application form.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Employed individuals</h3>\r\nA valid ID, business registration papers, and financial statements such as an ITR are required.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Overseas Filipino Workers (OFWs)</h3>\r\nPresent a passport, overseas employment proof, and authorization documents if a representative is opening the account.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Corporations or partnerships</h3>\r\nSubmit business registration documents, SEC/DTI certificates, and a board resolution authorizing the account opening.</li>\r\n</ol>'),
