(7338, 798, 'my_money_3_image_content_content_description', 'To apply, you must submit a valid ID, proof of income, and other necessary documents. Requirements may vary based on your employment status and loan terms.\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Employed individuals</h3>\r\nProvide a valid ID, latest payslips, and proof of employment. Payroll bank statements may be required for verification.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Self-employed individuals</h3>\r\nSubmit business registration papers, latest financial statements, and proof of income. Bank records may be needed to confirm cash flow.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Overseas Filipino Workers (OFWs)</h3>\r\nPresent a valid passport, employment contract, and remittance receipts. A Special Power of Attorney (SPA) may be necessary.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Corporations or partnerships</h3>\r\nProvide business permits, latest audited financial statements, and company registration documents. An authorization letter from company directors may be required.</li>\r\n</ol>'),
