(7486, 799, 'my_money_3_image_content_content_description', 'Applicants must present valid identification, proof of income, and relevant supporting documents. Additional paperwork may be required depending on the loan amount and borrower status.\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Employed individuals</h3>\r\nSubmit a valid ID, latest payslips, and Certificate of Employment. Additional financial documents may be required for verification.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Self-employed individuals</h3>\r\nProvide business registration papers, latest tax returns, and financial statements. Bank statements may be requested to assess repayment capacity.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Overseas Filipino Workers (OFWs)</h3>\r\nPresent a valid passport, employment contract, and remittance records. An SPA may be necessary for applications handled by a representative.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Corporations or partnerships</h3>\r\nSubmit business permits, company registration documents, and financial statements. A board resolution or authorization letter may also be required.</li>\r\n</ol>'),
