(7630, 498, 'my_money_3_image_content_content_description', 'A valid ID, proof of income, and supporting financial documents are needed to apply. Other requirements may be requested based on eligibility criteria.\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Employed individuals</h3>\r\nProvide a valid government ID, payslips, and proof of employment. Additional bank records may be required for high-value loans.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Self-employed individuals</h3>\r\nSubmit business registration, proof of earnings, and latest financial statements. Additional verification documents may be needed.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Overseas Filipino Workers (OFWs)</h3>\r\nPresent a valid passport, proof of remittances, and an employment contract. An SPA may be required for transactions made on your behalf.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Corporations or partnerships</h3>\r\nProvide business registration, audited financial reports, and authorization documents. Additional corporate records may be requested.</li>\r\n</ol>'),
