(7703, 867, '_form', '<div class=\"fowm_wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-12\">\n            <div class=\"header\">\n                <h3 class=\"mb-30\">Data Privacy Statement and Consent Form</h3>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-12\">\n            <div class=\"content\">\n                <p>The Bank of Makati (A Savings Bank), Inc. (BMI) recognizes its responsibilities under Republic Act\n                    No. 10173, also knowns as the Data Privacy Act of 2012. Personal data obtained from this digital\n                    platform is entered and stored within BMI\'s authorized information and communications system, and\n                    will only be accessed by BMI authorized personnel. BMI has instituted appropriate organizational,\n                    technical and physical security measures to ensure the protection of the personal data submitted\n                    herein. All collected personal data will be kept in accordance with BMI\'s retention policy. Users of\n                    this digital platform may exercise their privacy rights such as the right to be informed, right to\n                    object, right to rectification, right to erasure, right to file complaint, and right to damages. To\n                    know more about BMI\'s Data Privacy Statement, please visit <a href=\"www.bankofmakati.com.ph\"\n                        target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.bankofmakati.com.ph</a>.</p>\n                <p>By clicking on the \"I Agree\" button below, I consent to the use and processing of my information for\n                    the purpose of processing of my request for refund. I confirm that the information provided in this\n                    form is true, correct, and complete statement of the information contained herein. I understand that\n                    I may need to be contacted for further clarification, information or verification should there be\n                    noted issue/s on my request.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"form_fields\">\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col-md-12\">\n                    <div class=\"header\">\n                        <h4>Data Privacy and Consent</h4>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"col-md--12\">\n                    [acceptance consent-accept optional default:on] I Agree [/acceptance]\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>[cf7mls_step cf7mls_step-1 \"Next\" \"\"]<div class=\"form_wrapper\">\n    <h3>Borrower’s Information and Contact Details</h3>\n    <div class=\"form_field\">\n        [text* full_name placeholder \"Full Name\"]\n        [tel* primary_mobile_number placeholder \"Mobile Number (Required)\"]\n        [tel* secondary_mobile_number placeholder \"Secondary Contact Number\"]\n        [email* email placeholder \"Email address\"]\n    </div>\n    <p>Please ensure to submit Valid ID as listed in the <a href=\"\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\n            class=\"orange_text\">attached image</a>. Request with invalid supporting document/s may result to delay in\n        processing of request.</p>\n    [file* attached_image filetypes:image/* limit:1mb]\n</div>[cf7mls_step cf7mls_step-2 \"Back\" \"Next\" \"Step 3\"]<div class=\"form_wrapper\">\n    <h3>Account Information</h3>\n    <p>Please ensure to provide the correct account number. Request with invalid account number may result to delay in\n        processing of request.</p>\n    [number* account_number placeholder \"10 Digit Account Number (Required)\"]\n    <P>Please enter the maturity date stated in your Loan Payment Schedule / Statement of Account or Promissory Note</P>\n    [text* maturity_date id:maturity_date placeholder \"Maturity Date (Required)\" ]\n    <p>Please enter the Loan Term stated in your Loan Payment Schedule / Statement of Account or Promissory Note</p>\n    [select* loan_term firt_as_label \"Loan Term (Required)\" \"1 Year\" \"2 Years\" \"3 Years\" \"4 Years\" \"5 Years\" \"6 Years\"\n    \"7 Years\" \"8 Years\" \"9 Years\" \"10 Years\"]       \n    <div class=\"form_field\">\n        [number* loan_ammount_of_excess_payment placeholder\"Exact Amount Of Excess Payment (Required)\"]\n        [select* first_as_label \"Excess Payment Amount (Requested Amount for Refund) (Required)\" \"Equal to or less than P5,000\" \"More than P5,000\"]\n    </div>\n</div>[cf7mls_step cf7mls_step-3 \"Back\" \"Next\" \"Step 4\"]<div class=\"form_wrapper\">\n    <h3>Mode of Receipt</h3>\n    [select* mode_of_receipt first_as_label \"Please select your preferred mode of receipt (Required)\" \"Deposit to Account (Selected Banks)\" \"Issuance of Check\"]\n</div>[cf7mls_step cf7mls_step-4 \"Back\" \"Next\" \"Step 5\"][group deposite_to_account]\n<div class=\"form_wrapper\">\n    <h3>Deposit To Account</h3>\n    <div class=\"form_field\">\n        [select* bank \"Bank of Makati (A Savings Bank), Inc.\" \"Banco de Oro (BDO)\" \"Bank of the Philippine Island (BPI)\"\n        \"China Banking Corporation (Chinabank)\" \"East West Bank\" \"Metrobank\" \"Security Bank\" \"Philippine National Bank\n        (PNB)\" \"Rizal Commercial Banking Corporation (RCBC)\" \"Unionbank\"]\n        [text* bank_branch placeholder \"Bank Branch (Example - Dian Makati Branch) (Required)\"]\n        [number* bank_account_number placeholder \"Bank Account Number (Required)\"]\n        [select* type_of_account \"Type of Account (Required)\" \"Savings\" \"Current / Checking\"]\n    </div>\n    <p>Please make sure that the bank account name and account number provided are correct</p>\n    [acceptance confirmation] I confirm that the details are correct [/acceptance]\n</div>\n[/group]\n\n[group request_for_insurance]\n<div class=\"form_wrapper\">\n    <h3>Request for Issuance Of Check</h3>\n    [select* bmi_branch first_as_label \"Please sel