(8771, 818, 'my_money_3_image_content_content_description', 'To qualify, borrowers must provide valid IDs, proof of income, and property-related documents. Additional requirements may depend on the loan structure and applicant profile.\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Employed individuals</h3>\r\nSubmit a valid ID, payslips, and proof of employment. A credit evaluation may be conducted based on financial records.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Self-employed individuals</h3>\r\nProvide business registration, proof of revenue, and financial statements. Additional income documentation may be necessary.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Overseas Filipino Workers (OFWs)</h3>\r\nPresent a valid passport, proof of remittance, and employment contract. An SPA may be needed for applications made on your behalf.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Corporations or partnerships</h3>\r\nSubmit business permits, company registration, and proof of operations. A board resolution authorizing the loan application may also be required.</li>\r\n</ol>'),
