(991, 1, '2025-03-03 07:43:34', '2025-03-03 07:43:34', 'TEXT SCAM ALERT: We continue to receive reports of a scam involving text messages allegedly from Bank of Makati about raffle contests or prizes, discounts, refunds, stranded relatives and other fraudulent claims.\r\n\r\nBank of Makati does not engage in promotional text campaigns of this kind. If you receive a similar suspicious text message, please:\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Do not reply to the message.</li>\r\n 	<li>Report the suspicious text message by:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Forwarding it to 0922-878-8780</li>\r\n 	<li>Calling 889-0000 Local 902</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Block the number from which the suspicious text message came.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nThank you very much for your cooperation.', 'TEXT SCAM ALERT', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'text-scam-alert-26', '', '', '2025-03-03 07:43:34', '2025-03-03 07:43:34', '', 0, 'https://bankofmakati.innovnational.com/?post_type=news&#038;p=991', 24, 'news', '', 0),
