(1008, 1, '2025-03-03 07:54:17', '2025-03-03 07:54:17', '<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1009\" src=\"https://bankofmakati.innovnational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Grace-Park-Branch-Opening-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1978\" />\r\n\r\nBank of Makati recently launched its 62nd branch in Grace Park-Caloocan City, the second branch to be inaugurated this year.\r\n\r\nLeading the simple inauguration ceremonies last March 24, 2017 were Branch Banking Group Head Angel G. Muyot Jr. and Area Manager Alvin Del Ponso, with guests Benita Cheng and Shalani Soledad-Romulo.\r\n\r\nThe opening of the Grace Park-Caloocan branch came on the heels of the launch of BMI\'s Legazpi branch last March 20. Twenty-two other branches were launched in 2016, namely, Marikina, Dasmariñas (Cavite), Tacloban, La Union, Biñan (Laguna), Muntinlupa, Baliuag (Bulacan), Valenzuela, Las Piñas, Rodriguez (Rizal), Daet (Camarines Norte), Tagum (Davao), Pagadian City (Zamboanga del Sur), Calapan City (Oriental Mindoro), Butuan City (Agusan del Norte), Valencia (Bukidnon), Lucena (Quezon), Zamboanga, Balanga (Bataan), Urdaneta (Pangasinan), Buendia (Makati) and Gensan (South Cotabato).\r\n\r\nThe newest branch is manned by Branch Operation Head Mary Ann Marasigan, Branch Relations Officer Minerva Belen and Alternate Teller Crizelle Aliwalas.\r\n\r\nIt is located at VSP Condominium 1607-C Rizal Avenue Extension, Grace Park, Caloocan City, with phone numbers 288-3206 and 288-2663.', 'Grace Park - Caloocan branch becomes BMI\'s 62nd', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'grace-park-caloocan-branch-becomes-bmis-62nd-3', '', '', '2025-03-03 07:54:17', '2025-03-03 07:54:17', '', 0, 'https://bankofmakati.innovnational.com/?post_type=news&#038;p=1008', 12, 'news', '', 0),
