(1010, 1, '2025-03-03 07:55:25', '2025-03-03 07:55:25', 'Bank of Makati\'s Legazpi City branch was inaugurated as BMI\'s 61st branch on March 20, 2017.\r\n\r\nLeading the simple inauguration rites were BMI Branch Banking Group Head Angel G. Muyot, Jr. and Area Head Socorro R. Yabut with guests Legazpi City Mayor Noel E. Rosal and Albay 2nd District Congressman Joey Sarte Salceda.\r\n\r\nThe Legazpi branch was the first to be inaugurated this year, and the 23rd since 2016. Inaugurated in 2016 were branches in Marikina, Dasmariñas (Cavite), Tacloban, La Union, Biñan (Laguna), Muntinlupa, Baliuag (Bulacan), Valenzuela, Las Piñas, Rodriguez (Rizal), Daet (Camarines Norte), Tagum (Davao), Pagadian City (Zamboanga del Sur), Calapan City (Oriental Mindoro), Butuan City (Agusan del Norte), Valencia (Bukidnon), Lucena (Quezon), Zamboanga, Balanga (Bataan), Urdaneta (Pangasinan), Buendia (Makati) and Gensan (South Cotabato).\r\n\r\nManning the latest addition to BMI\'s network of regular branches are Branch Manager Jeth M. Molato, Roving Branch Operation Head Ramoncito P. Boton, Loan Supervisor Myra Orense, Loan Processor Janeth Lacre, Account Officer Rodrigo Mark Requiza and Teller Danica Olila.\r\n\r\nThe Legazpi branch is located at Imperial Shopping Plaza, Los Baños Avenue, Capantawan, Legazpi City, Albay, with phone numbers 0933-400-8991 and 0905-507-1436.', 'BMI\'s 61st branch opens in Legazpi City', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bmis-61st-branch-opens-in-legazpi-city-4', '', '', '2025-04-14 01:13:51', '2025-04-14 01:13:51', '', 0, 'https://bankofmakati.innovnational.com/?post_type=news&#038;p=1010', 11, 'news', '', 0),
