(1012, 1, '2025-03-03 07:56:02', '2025-03-03 07:56:02', 'Bank of Makati ended 2016 with the launch of its Marikina branch, its 60th nationwide. It was a fitting close to BMI\'s 60th year in the industry.\r\n\r\nLeading the simple inauguration rites on December 29, 2016 were BMI President Ma. Rodora E. Bañares, Branch Banking Group Head Angel G. Muyot Jr., Branch Manager Emylyn S. Sta. Ana with guests, Councilor Donn Favis, Medy Domingo and Lydia Pajares.\r\n\r\nThe Marikina branch was the 22nd to be inaugurated in 2016, following the launch of branches in Dasmariñas (Cavite), Tacloban, La Union, Biñan (Laguna), Muntinlupa, Baliuag (Bulacan), Valenzuela, Las Piñas, Rodriguez (Rizal), Daet (Camarines Norte), Tagum (Davao), Pagadian City (Zamboanga del Sur), Calapan City (Oriental Mindoro), Butuan City (Agusan del Norte), Valencia (Bukidnon), Lucena (Quezon), Zamboanga, Balanga (Bataan), Urdaneta (Pangasinan), Buendia (Makati) and Gensan (South Cotabato)\r\n\r\nManning the latest addition to BMI\'s network of regular branches are Branch Manager Emylyn Sta. Ana, Branch Operations Head Norlyn G. Maranan and Teller Mariel May H. Chavez.\r\n\r\nThe Marikina branch is located at 19 Bayan-Bayanan Ave., Concepcion I, Marikina City, with telephone numbers (02) 721-8238, 721-8244, 0933-629-7895 and 0942-376-0844.', 'BMI closes 2016 with 60th branch in Marikina', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bmi-closes-2016-with-60th-branch-in-marikina', '', '', '2025-03-03 07:56:02', '2025-03-03 07:56:02', '', 0, 'https://bankofmakati.innovnational.com/?post_type=news&#038;p=1012', 10, 'news', '', 0),
(1013, 1, '2025-03-03 07:56:59', '2025-03-03 07:56:59', '<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1014\" src=\"https://bankofmakati.innovnational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Dasma-Branch-Opening2-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1978\" />\r\n\r\nBank of Makati recently opened its Dasmariñas, Cavite branch, it\'s 59th branch nationwide. The branch had a soft launch in December 28, 2016 and formal dedication rites in January 10, 2017.\r\n\r\nLeading the dedication rites were BMI Branch Banking Group Head Angel G. Muyot Jr., and Manolito A. Jaro, property owner, as guest.\r\n\r\nThe Dasmariñas branch was the 21st to be inaugurated in 2016, following the launch of branches in Tacloban, La Union, Biñan (Laguna), Muntinlupa, Baliuag (Bulacan), Valenzuela, Las Piñas, Rodriguez (Rizal), Daet (Camarines Norte), Tagum (Davao), Pagadian City (Zamboanga del Sur), Calapan City (Oriental Mindoro), Butuan City (Agusan del Norte), Valencia (Bukidnon), Lucena (Quezon), Zamboanga, Balanga (Bataan), Urdaneta (Pangasinan), Buendia (Makati) and Gensan (South Cotabato). Manning the branch are Frederick Locsin (Branch Manager), Helen Marizel D. de Ocampo (Branch Operations Head), Edrian P. Lacorte (Branch Relations Officer), Ryan M. Achas (Account Officer), Michelle Lyn M. Caratao (Loan Documentation Supervisor), Elizabeth G. De Taza (Loan Processor) and Ivy B. Alipar (Teller).\r\n\r\nThe Dasmariñas branch is located at B55 L7 Golden Miles Molino - Paliparan Road Brgy. Salawag, Dasmariñas City, with phone numbers (046) 424-2168 and 0925-610-2350.', 'BMI opens 59th branch in Dasmariñas, Cavite', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bmi-opens-59th-branch-in-dasmarinas-cavite-6', '', '', '2025-03-03 07:56:59', '2025-03-03 07:56:59', '', 0, 'https://bankofmakati.innovnational.com/?post_type=news&#038;p=1013', 9, 'news', '', 0),
