(1018, 1, '2025-03-03 07:59:54', '2025-03-03 07:59:54', '<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1019\" src=\"https://bankofmakati.innovnational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/butuan-branch-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1978\" />\r\n\r\nBank of Makati (A Savings Bank), Inc. now has a full-service branch in Butuan City, following the conversion of its Butuan loan center. The Butuan branch was inaugurated in simple ceremonies led by BMI Branch Banking Group Head Angel C. Muyot, Jr. and client Atty. Roger C. Realis of Realis Law and Consultancy Agency on April 4, 2016.\r\n\r\nThe Butuan Branch is BMI\'s 46th branch. Also converted into regular branches in late 2015 to early March this year were the loan centers in Valencia (Bukidnon), Lucena (Quezon), Zamboanga, Balanga (Bataan), Urdaneta (Pangasinan), Bacolod, Cagayan de Oro, Santiago (Isabela), Laoag (Ilocos Norte) and Batangas. More loan centers are expected to follow suit, in accordance with the Bangko Sentral ng Pilipinas approval last July of the conversion of all 24 BMI Loan Centers into regular branches.\r\n\r\nThe Butuan branch is manned by Branch Manager Joel Cabusao, Branch Operations Head Jinky Bayeta, Loans Supervisor Kim Patal, Loans Processor Kezia Pospos, Relationship Officer Alvan Babano, Account Officer Joener Calva, and Teller Hannah Mae Cinco.\r\n\r\nThe newest BMI branch is located at Lucibenino Building, JC Aquino Ave., Butuan City, Agusan del Sur, with phone numbers (085) 225-9583 and 0949-698-4026.', 'BMI Now Operates Full-Service Branch in Butuan City', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bmi-now-operates-full-service-branch-in-butuan-city-10', '', '', '2025-03-03 08:00:01', '2025-03-03 08:00:01', '', 0, 'https://bankofmakati.innovnational.com/?post_type=news&#038;p=1018', 6, 'news', '', 0),
