(1020, 1, '2025-03-03 08:02:17', '2025-03-03 08:02:17', '<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1019\" src=\"https://bankofmakati.innovnational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/butuan-branch-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1978\" />\r\n\r\nBank of Makati\'s Biñan branch became the 56th in BMI\'s nationwide network, with its inauguration on October 14, 2016.\r\n\r\nThe Biñan branch was the 18th to be inaugurated this year, following the launch of branches in Muntinlupa, Baliuag (Bulacan), Valenzuela, Las Piñas, Rodriguez (Rizal), Daet (Camarines Norte), Tagum (Davao), Pagadian City (Zamboanga del Sur), Calapan City (Oriental Mindoro), Butuan City (Agusan del Norte), Valencia (Bukidnon), Lucena (Quezon), Zamboanga, Balanga (Bataan), Urdaneta (Pangasinan), Buendia (Makati) and Gensan (South Cotabato).\r\n\r\nLeading the simple inauguration rites were Branch Banking Group Head Angel G. Muyot, Jr. and Area Head Socorro R. Yabut, with guests, Donaldo Ducot, Owner of Haddassah Academy in San Pedro, Laguna, and Jasmin Alonte, Chief of Staff of the Biñan City Mayor\'s Office.\r\n\r\nThe Biñan branch is manned by Federico F. Jimenez (Branch Manager), Rowena S. Bacay (Branch Operation Head), Ann Marie Bigay (Area Loan Operation Officer), Rejean L. Cabral (Branch Relationship Officer), Ramuelito Valeroso (Account Officer), and Joanna Marie Pescasio and Syka Mae Julian (Tellers).\r\n\r\nThe Biñan branch is located at A. Bonifacio St., Biñan, Laguna, with phone numbers, (02) 519-7563 to 64.', 'BMI\'s 56th branch inaugurated in Biñan', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bmis-56th-branch-inaugurated-in-binan-9', '', '', '2025-03-03 08:02:41', '2025-03-03 08:02:41', '', 0, 'https://bankofmakati.innovnational.com/?post_type=news&#038;p=1020', 5, 'news', '', 0),
