acy Act of 2012 are violated, you may send us an email through our privacy concern email address privacyconcern@bankofmakati.com.ph, and give us a chance to correct the possible violation.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>How We Protect Your Personal Information</h2>\r\nOur technology and information security framework, which undergoes continuous assessment to improve in securing your privacy, shall prevent unauthorized access to your information. Our oversight risk management department, monitors the risk appetite of the Bank to ensure that we are in compliance with the regulators and does not violate the rights of clients.\r\n<div class=\"row align-items-center\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-8\">\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<h2>Contact Our Data Protection Officer (DPO)</h2>\r\nFor any privacy concern, you may reach our Data Protection Officer through the following means: <strong>Email</strong>: privacyconcern@bankofmakati.com.ph <strong>Contact</strong> No: 8889-0000 loc. 1113 or 1601 09255-256683 <strong>Address</strong>: The Data Protection Officer – Bank of Makati (A Savings Bank), Inc. Bank of Makati Bldg. Ayala Ave Extension near cor Metropolitan Ave, Brgy. Bel-air, Makati City\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-4\">\r\n<div class=\"image\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1156\" src=\"https://bankofmakati.innovnational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/dpo.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"380\" height=\"700\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Data Privacy Statement', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-06-20 02:19:43', '2025-06-20 02:19:43', '', 3, 'https://bankofmakati.innovnational.com/?p=1164', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
