hers (please specify)\"]\r\n\r\n[text others_specify1 class:others_specify1 readonly placeholder \"Others (please specify)\"]\r\n\r\n<span class=\"d-block black_text title_text\">Other Pre-application Requirements</span>\r\n\r\n[checkbox other_pre_app class:other_pre_app use_label_element \"Billing statement of utilities for the past 3 months\" \"Statement of Account from current lender and official receipts for the past 3 months (if loan purpose is refinancing/loan takeout)\" \"Others (please specify)\"]\r\n\r\n[text others_specify2 class:others_specify2 readonly placeholder \"Others (please specify)\"]\r\n\r\n<span class=\"d-block black_text title_text\">Security Documents (Please check applicable item/s)</span>\r\n\r\n[checkbox security_docs class:security_docs use_label_element \"Photocopy of Transfer Certificate of Title (TCT)/Condominium Certificate of Title (CCT)\" \"Photocopy of Tax Declaration (for land and improvement)\" \"Location/Vicinity Map\" \"Land Transportation Office (LTO) Official Receipt (OR)/Certificate of Registration (CR) or Deed of Sale of Motor Vehicle\" \"Reservation Agreement or Contract to Sell or Statement of Account (for Deed of Assignment (DOA) accounts only)\"]\r\n\r\n<span class=\"d-block black_text\">If secured by a Continuing Suretyship:</span>\r\n\r\n[checkbox if_secured class:if_secured use_label_element \"Basic Documents (as enumerated in this form) of the surety\" \"Income Documents (as enumerated in this form) of the Surety\"]\r\n\r\n<span class=\"d-block black_text\">If construction loan</span>\r\n\r\n[checkbox if_construction_loan class:if_construction_loan use_label_element \"Building/Floor plan of proposed improvement\" \"Bill of Materials\" \"Specification of proposed finishes\" \"Building permit\"]\r\n\r\n<span class=\"d-block black_text\">If refinancing/loan take out</span>\r\n\r\n[checkbox if_refinancing class:if_refinancing use_label_element \"Statement of Account from current lender and official receipts for the past 3 months\"]\r\n\r\n<span class=\"d-block black_text\">Others</span>\r\n\r\n[checkbox security_docs_others class:security_docs_others use_label_element \"Appraisal fee\" \"Additional security documents (please specify)\"]\r\n\r\n[text add_sec_docs class:add_sec_docs readonly placeholder \"Additional security documents (please specify)\"]\r\n\r\n<span class=\"d-block black_text title_text\">Post-approval requirements for real estate collateral-backed loans (Please check applicable item/s)</span>\r\n\r\n[checkbox post_approval class:post_approval use_label_element \"Original owner’s copy of TCT/CCT\" \"Original Tax Clearance\" \"Certified true copy of latest Tax Declaration\" \"Insurance policy/ies (for properties with improvements)\" \"Master Deed of Declaration (for condominium only)\" \"Photocopy of latest full year Real Estate Tax Receipt (RETR)\" \"Price quotation of the property (for property acquisition)\" \"Affidavit of Consent to Mortgage Family Home\" \"Others (please specify)\"]\r\n\r\n[text others_specify3 class:others_specify3 readonly placeholder \"Others (please specify)\"]\r\n\r\n<span class=\"d-block black_text title_text\">Other post-approval requirements</span>\r\n\r\n[checkbox post_approval_other class:post_approval_other use_label_element \"General Information Sheet (GIS), if applicable\" \"Special Power of Attorney, if applicable\" \"Certificate of Ownership for movable property (e.g., motor vehicles, etc.)\"]\r\n\r\n[submit class:orange_btn \"Submit\"]\r\n</div>[cf7mls_step cf7mls_step-6 \"Back\" \"Step 6\"]\n1\n[_site_title] Individual and Sole Proprietorship\n[_site_title] <wordpress@bankofmakati.innovnational.com>\n[_site_admin_email], mae.mariano@seo-hacker.net\nFrom: [your-name] [your-email]\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 1</strong>\r\n<strong>Personal Information</strong>\r\n\r\nApplication type: [application_type]\r\nType of Borrower: [type_borrower]\r\n\r\nName of Borrower: [borrower_name]\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 2</strong>\r